        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1697114551" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer496584844784384028">I am confoundingly happy that poets can also be great novelists. (I read very little poetry, dedicating my time to prose almost exclusively.) Better yet, sometimes expert autobiographers.<br/><br/>Shares the same bookshelf with Jeanette Walls&apos; also mighty impressive nonfiction autobio &quot;The Glass Castle.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText496584844784384028" style="display:none">I am confoundingly happy that poets can also be great novelists. (I read very little poetry, dedicating my time to prose almost exclusively.) Better yet, sometimes expert autobiographers.<br /><br />Shares the same bookshelf with Jeanette Walls' also mighty impressive nonfiction autobio "The Glass Castle."</span>
