        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer704740911" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8148157628216542727">What a book. Mary Karr is salty and funny and brilliant and fierce. Such a big, big voice. She even made the last section work--and I was skeptical about a time jump. Fuck the haters who call this just another &quot;misery memoir.&quot; It&apos;s too funny to be truly miserable. There&apos;s a reason why people still read this memoir decades later.</span>
  <span id="freeText8148157628216542727" style="display:none">What a book. Mary Karr is salty and funny and brilliant and fierce. Such a big, big voice. She even made the last section work--and I was skeptical about a time jump. Fuck the haters who call this just another "misery memoir." It's too funny to be truly miserable. There's a reason why people still read this memoir decades later.</span>
